Scroll of Reckoning
By the time he looked up, it was too late. 
The world outside his screen had moved on without him.
A plea, scrawled in shaky letters—asking for one more chance, 
one more moment. But some things can’t be reset. Some things can’t be won back. 
And all he could do was watch as everything he ignored faded away. 
He now enters the Underwolrd, to atone for his sins
